Hi All,<br />
<br />
I'm trying to run RazorEngine from VB.net.<br />
<br />
I've added the following to my web.config...<br />
<pre><code>  &lt;configSections&gt;
    &lt;section name=&quot;razorEngine&quot; type=&quot;RazorEngine.Configuration.RazorEngineConfigurationSection, RazorEngine&quot; requirePermission=&quot;false&quot;/&gt;
  &lt;/configSections&gt;
  &lt;razorEngine&gt;
    &lt;templateServices&gt;
      &lt;add name=&quot;myCustomTemplateService&quot; language=&quot;VisualBasic&quot;/&gt;
    &lt;/templateServices&gt;
  &lt;/razorEngine&gt;</code></pre>

... as per the <a href="http://razorengine.codeplex.com/wikipage?title=Using%20Configuration" rel="nofollow">documentation</a>, but it's giving an error on the line...<br />
<pre><code>&lt;add name=&quot;myCustomTemplateService&quot; language=&quot;VisualBasic&quot;/&gt;</code></pre>

Parser Error Message: Unrecognized element 'add'.<br />
<br />
Can anyone tell me what I'm doing wrong? Is there something else I have to add to my project, or web.config etc?<br />
<br />
